data.eml:eml: New or little-known Diamesinae (Diptera: Chironomidae) from Oriental China

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Sun, Bingjiao, Lin, Xiaolong, Wang, Xinhua, Makarchenko, Eugenyi A. (2019): New or little-known Diamesinae (Diptera: Chironomidae) from Oriental China. Zootaxa 4571 (4): 544-550, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4571.4.6
